snippet: New York Jets coach Todd Bowles was hospitalized Friday with what the team called an "undisclosed illness," and he did not travel for the game at New England on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: New York Jets coach Todd Bowles was hospitalized Friday with what the team called an "undisclosed illness," and he did not travel for the game at New England on Saturday.

headline.main: Jets Coach Bowles Hospitalized, Doesn't Travel With Team
headline.print_headline: Jets Coach Bowles Hospitalized, Doesn't Travel With Team
